REFERRED TO CORPORATIONS, AUTHORITIES AND COMMISSIONS

Title: Provides for unlisted telephone numbers without charge for victims of domestic violence for whose benefit an order of protection has been issued
Summary: Provides for unlisted telephone directory numbers without charge, for victims of domestic violence for whose benefit an order of protection has been issued by a court of competent jurisdiction.
LawCode: Amd ยง91, Pub Serv L
ActClause: AN ACT to amend the public service law, in relation to providing for unlisted telephone numbers without charge for certain victims of domestic violence
